Munyayi  munhu anoshanda semutumwa achifambisa mashoko pakati pemhuri mbiri dziri kuroorerana. Nguva dzose munyai munhu wechirume anosarudzwa kumhuri yemurume ari kunoroora. Munyayi ndiye anononzwa kuti [[tezvara]] ari kutema pfuma yakawanda sei, achizoturikira mashoko aya kune mukwasha auya kuzoroora. Munyayi ndiye zvakare anodzosa mhinduro dzezvichemo kana kubvumira kwe[[mukuwasha]].

Pakubata basa iri, munyai anobatsirwa na[[tete]] vemusikana vanofanirwa kunge vachiziva tsika dzemusha waberekwa musikana uye vachiziva vanhu vemo kuitira pakutaura ukama hwevanhu kana vasangana mhuri mbiri. 

Kune mamwe matunhu munyayi anodainzwa kunzi [[sadunzvi]] kana kuti [[dunzvi]]

In English "munyayi" is a go-between when a man goes to pay the bride price at her future wife's family.

